Task Evaluation Questionnaire

Please think back to earlier in the experiment, when you were required to repeat, outloud the word {{text}} for 20 second. How did you feel after repeating the word? To respond, please rate each question below using the numbers from 1 to 7, whereby 1 indicates tha your strongly disagree with the statement, while 7 signifies a strong agreement with the statement.
I felt I'd let myself down
For this question, please select the number <u>2</u>
